org.nd4j.linalg.api.complex

Interface IComplexNumber

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IComplexDouble, IComplexFloat
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseComplexDouble, BaseComplexFloat, ComplexDouble, ComplexDouble, ComplexFloat, ComplexFloat

    public interface IComplexNumber
    Baseline interface for a complex number with realComponent and imaginary components.

    Based off of the jblas api by mikio braun
